lyrics:
Добро!
Я люблю печь печеньки
И раздавать их всем вокруг!
ураааа!

[verse]
Darkness surrounds Доброта, our guiding light
In the chaos we find solace, our souls ignite
Raging flames of compassion, burning strong and bright
A force that defies the shadows, relentless might

[chorus]
Доброта, the epitome of strength and grace
A symphony of brutality, eradicating hate
Through the thunderous roars, forever we'll embrace
Доброта, forevermore, our savior we venerate
